"Indítjuk a Helyválasztót. \n A CityApp használatához először egy vizsgálati helyszínt kell választani: \n \n 1.First have to add an area (such as country) to the dataset.\n If you do not want to add a new area, you may skip this step.\n Adding a new area may take a long time, depending on the file size.\n 2. Zoom to the sub-area of your interest, then use Polygon drawing tool to exactly define that.\n 3. Save your selection, name it, define the resolution and close the window. \n \n Now, if you are ready to add a new area to the dataset, click -- Yes -- \n If you only want to refine your selection, without adding a new area, click -- No -- \n To leave Cityapp click -- Cancel --"
